item.title: CVE-2017-16773|2024-09-17T00:10:52.432Z -- synology -- universal%20search
item.description: Improper authorization vulnerability in Highlight Preview in Synology Universal Search before 1.0.5-0135 allows remote authenticated users to bypass permission checks for directories in POSIX mode.
